---
title: Crispy Chicken with New Potatoes and a Leek & Tarragon Sauce
description: Our chefs have been creating recipes for a while now and one thing they’ve learnt along the way is that chicken, tarragon and cream are a flavour combination that our customers absolutely love. And because time should never stand in the way of a delicious meal, our chef’s have created a superquick recipe that contains all the flavours you can’t get enough of! We’ll send your compliments to the chef!  For further information on Flora, please visit: https://www.flora.com/products/flora-original/
